div>\n<div> 2011年 12月 07日</div>\n<h2>时事大家谈：盲人律师陈光诚的近况与中国人权</h2>\n<div>\n<p><span>美国之音张佩芝</span>  </p>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"20\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-email.gif\" width=\"20\" /></a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"20\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-printer.gif\" width=\"20\" /></a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20111207-Issues-and-Opinions-China-Human-Rights-and-Chen-Guangcheng-135165178.html#comments\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"20\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-comments.gif\" width=\"20\" /></a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.google.com/buzz/post?message=%E6%97%B6%E4%BA%8B%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E8%B0%88%EF%BC%9A%E7%9B%B2%E4%BA%BA%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%88%E9%99%88%E5%85%89%E8%AF%9A%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%91%E5%86%B5%E4%B8%8E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E4%BA%BA%E6%9D%83&#038;url=http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20111207-Issues-and-Opinions-China-Human-Rights-and-Chen-Guangcheng-135165178.html\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-googleBuzz.png\" /></a></li>\n<li>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\"></a></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://twitthis.com/twit?url=http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20111207-Issues-and-Opinions-China-Human-Rights-and-Chen-Guangcheng-135165178.html&#038;title=%E6%97%B6%E4%BA%8B%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E8%B0%88%EF%BC%9A%E7%9B%B2%E4%BA%BA%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%88%E9%99%88%E5%85%89%E8%AF%9A%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%91%E5%86%B5%E4%B8%8E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E4%BA%BA%E6%9D%83\"></a></li>\n<li>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div>\n<p>因揭发山东临沂当地官员暴力推行计划生育政策而遭到迫害中国盲人维权律师陈光诚的现况受到国际社会的密切注意。国际人权组织不断呼吁中国解除对陈光诚的软禁，美国国会还针对陈光诚案举行听众会，还有资深议员希望能率领议员代表团希望亲自到山东临沂探访陈光诚。</p>\n<p>在今天节目里，我们请到“女权无疆界”组织总裁瑞洁(Reggie Littlejohn)，和我们共同关注陈光诚的现况，以及围绕陈光诚案的中国人权问题。</p>\n<p><strong>视频第一部分：</strong></p>\n<p><span></span></p>\n<div>\n<div>\n<span></span></div>\n<p><strong>视频第二部分：</strong></p>\n<div>\n<div>\n<span></span></div>\n<p><span><br /></span></p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<h4>相关文章</h4>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<h3><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20111207-BLIND-RIGHTS-ACTIVIST-135172353.html\">陈光诚支持者再被旅游 网友被拘临沂仍无消息</a> <img align=\"top\" border=\"0\" height=\"10\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-media-audio.gif\" width=\"14\" /><img align=\"top\" border=\"0\" height=\"10\" src=\"http://media.voanews.com/designimages/icon-media-comment-gray.gif\" width=\"12\" /></h3>\n<p>有报道称被非法软禁的中国盲人维权人士陈光诚处境在国内外舆论压力下略有改善之际，又有多名曾多次前往山东临沂声援的中国公民在不同城市遭到警方拘留或监控。</p>\n<div>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20111206-dc-supporters-chen-guangcheng-135111458.html\">美国会听证会：传陈光诚软禁境况略有改善</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20111206-dc-supporters-135100198.html\">声援陈光诚维权人士拉横幅被拘</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/201111122-uncut-news-134314803.html\">国际关注中国异议人士是帮倒忙？</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/javascript://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/openMoreSideContent('98','%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A',%20'%E6%9B%B4%E5%B0%91')\" name=\"sideContentMoreLink98\">更多</a></div>\n<div>\n<h4>相关链接</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLC04DC8A9F86FC9C3\">YouTube链接：时事大家谈：盲人律师陈光诚的近况与中国人权</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://mrss.dokoda.jp/r/http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/special-reports/world-and-regional/20111031-profile-cheng-guangcheng-132917023.html\">专题报道：探访陈光诚</a></li>\n<li><a 